east%2Fisrael-kills-mohammad-abu-itiwi-hamas-commander-involved-in-october-7-attack%2Famp_articleshow%2F114565016.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20Running%20To%20Be%20An%20American%20Tyrant%26quot%3B%3A%20Singer%20Bruce%20Springsteen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBruce%20Springsteen%20took%20the%20stage%20Thursday%20at%20Kamala%20Harris's%20star-studded%20campaign%20rally%20in%20swing%20state%20Georgia%2C%20with%20the%20rock%20legend%20warning%20that%20White%20House%20hopeful%20Donald%20Trump%20aims%20to%20be%20an%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20tyrant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20is%20cranking%20up%20the%20celebrity%20wattage%20--%20including%20with%20Beyonce%20in%20Texas%20on%20Friday%2C%20according%20to%20reports%20--%20at%20a%20series%20of%20concerts%20in%20battleground%20states%20to%20boost%20support%20in%20the%20final%20days%20of%20a%20nail-biting%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThursday's%20rally%20in%20Atlanta%20is%20also%20Harris's%20first%20campaign%20stop%20with%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20the%20only%20Black%20president%20in%20American%20history%20and%20who%20remains%20widely%20popular%20with%20Democratic%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20Springsteen's%20gritty%20commentary%20at%20the%20start%20that%20echoed%20through%20the%20packed%20rally%2C%20where%20the%20iconic%20singer%20said%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Boppose%26quot%3B%20the%20Republican%20former%20president%20because%20%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20is%20running%20to%20be%20an%20American%20tyrant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarge%20numbers%20of%20Americans%2C%20including%20about%202.2%20million%20in%20Georgia%2C%20have%20already%20cast%20ballots%20in%20early%20voting%2C%20reflecting%20intense%20engagement%20ahead%20of%20Election%20Day%20on%20November%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpringsteen%20brought%20his%20brand%20of%20socially%20conscious%2C%20working-class%20anthems%20including%20%26quot%3BThe%20Promised%20Land%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20out%20the%20vote%20and%20bolster%20Harris's%20blue-collar%20credentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vice%20president%20herself%20had%20raised%20the%20stakes%20further%20in%20a%20CNN%20appearance%20late%20Wednesday%20when%20she%20said%20she%20considers%2078-year-old%20Trump%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bfascist%26quot%3B%20--%20as%20charged%20in%20a%20bombshell%20interview%20by%20the%20Republican's%20former%20chief%20of%20staff%20John%20Kelly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20the%20oldest%20major%20presidential%20nominee%20in%20US%20history%20and%20the%20first%20to%20be%20running%20with%20a%20criminal%20record%2C%20is%20also%20casting%20the%20election%20as%20an%20existential%20battle%20for%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20will%20have%20profound%20personal%20implications%20too%2C%20given%20he%20is%20the%20subject%20of%20serious%20criminal%20probes%20into%20his%20attempt%20to%20overturn%20his%202020%20election%20loss%20and%20his%20post-presidential%20hoarding%20of%20top-secret%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%20was%20campaigning%20Thursday%20in%20the%20western%20battleground%20of%20Arizona%20where%20he%20conjured%20dark%20imagery%20of%20migrant%20violence%20and%20warned%20that%20America%20had%20become%20%26quot%3Ba%20dumping%20ground%26quot%3B%20for%20dangerous%20and%20undocumented%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20like%20a%20garbage%20can%20for%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Revenge'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20radio%20interview%20on%20his%20way%20to%20the%20rally%20in%20Arizona%20and%20then%20another%20in%20Nevada%20--%20both%20swing%20states%20--%20Trump%20announced%20that%20if%20elected%20he'd%20fire%20the%20special%20prosecutor%20overseeing%20his%20remaining%20cases%20in%20%26quot%3Bseconds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%2C%2060%2C%20for%20her%20part%20assailed%20Trump%20for%20%26quot%3Bplotting%20revenge%20and%20retribution%26quot%3B%20against%20his%20political%20enemies%2C%20and%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20his%20energy%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sad%20part%20about%20that%20is%20he's%20trying%20to%20be%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%20--%20probably%20the%20toughest%20job%20in%20the%20world%20--%20and%20he's%20exhausted%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20remains%20a%20toss-up%2C%20with%20the%20two%20candidates%20jostling%20within%20the%20margin%20of%20error%20in%20polls%20from%20all%20the%20swing%20states%20set%20to%20tip%20the%20overall%20national%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20media%20reported%20Thursday%20that%20Beyonce%20--%20whose%20hit%20%26quot%3BFreedom%26quot%3B%20is%20already%20the%20Harris%20campaign's%20signature%20song%20--%20will%20join%20the%20Democrat%20when%20she%20visits%20Houston%20on%20Friday%20to%20highlight%20abortion%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObama%2C%2063%2C%20has%20been%20making%20his%20own%20headlining%20appearances%20in%20support%20of%20Harris%20in%20a%20slew%20of%20swing%20states%2C%20including%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Wisconsin%20and%20Michigan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Harris%20campaign%20hopes%20the%20former%20president%20will%20reverse%20fears%20of%20eroding%20support%20among%20Black%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%2C%2060%2C%20is%20of%20mixed%20Black%20and%20South%20Asian%20heritage%2C%20and%20is%20vying%20to%20become%20the%20country's%20first%20female%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20American%20Dream%20'unreachable%20'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20expected%20to%20attack%20Harris's%20economic%20policies%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Tempe%2C%20Arizona.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20campaign%20said%20the%20current%20vice%20president%20had%20%26quot%3Bmade%20the%20American%20Dream%20of%20home%20ownership%20unreachable%20for%20young%20Americans%20and%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20his%2055-minute%20address%20Trump%20made%20zero%20mention%20of%20soaring%20housing%20costs%2C