igns%20and%20systems%2C%20making%20them%20a%20relatively%20riskier%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20a%20learning%20curve%20because%20some%20of%20these%20technologies%20are%20not%20mature%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20Buongiorno%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b22c795-2c48-4282-8e9c-8728dc854c1e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrioritize%20'earlier%20access%20to%20power'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20internal%20Amazon%20document%20described%20the%20company's%20nuclear%20initiatives%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20%26quot%3Bnon-standard%26quot%3B%20energy%20plan.%20The%20company%20also%20looked%20into%20power%20arrangements%20for%20natural%20gas%20plants%20and%20geothermal%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20drive%20development%20of%20first%20of%20a%20kind%2C%20non-standard%20energy%20sources%20within%20the%20industry%2C%20our%20scope%20is%20primarily%20medium%20to%20long%20term%2C%20supplying%20power%20in%20large%20amounts%20beyond%202030%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Amazon's%20goal%20is%20to%20deliver%208%20gigawatts%20of%20incremental%20renewable%20energy%2C%20the%20document%20said.%20Amazon%20reached%204.1%20gigawatts%20of%20renewable%20energy%20in%202023%20and%2010.2%20gigawatts%20in%202022%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20internal%20document%20listed%20the%20main%20%26quot%3Btenets%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20Global%20Energy%20Strategy%20team%20follows.%20It%20emphasized%20delivering%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20reliable%2C%20cost-effective%26quot%3B%20power%20on%20time%2C%20and%20making%20bets%20on%20technologies%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20cusp%20of%20scaling%20and%20mass%20adoption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20find%20the%20earliest%20available%20power%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20target%20obtaining%20large%20amounts%20of%20power%20over%20time%2C%20we%20will%20prioritize%20opportunities%20with%20the%20earlier%20access%20to%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20at%20Amazon%3F%20Got%20a%20tip%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EContact%20the%20reporter%2C%20Eugene%20Kim%2C%20via%20the%20encrypted-messaging%20apps%20Signal%20or%20Telegram%20(%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B1-650-942-3061%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%2B1-650-942-3061%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E)%20or%20email%20(%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aekim%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eekim%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E).%20Reach%20out%20using%20a%20nonwork%20device.%20Check%20out%20Business%20Insider's%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Esource%20guide%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20for%20other%20tips%20on%20sharing%20information%20securely.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nuclear-power-strategy-ai-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729812393000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712783101ea6d83dee2303e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nuclear-power-strategy-ai-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amazon%20is%20trying%20to%20use%20nuclear%20as%20a%20reliable%2C%20clean%20solution%20to%20meet%20AI's%20insatiable%20power%20demands.%20An%20internal%20document%20reveals%20new