r%20that%20cradles%20the%20head%20and%20neck%20and%20reduces%20pressure%20on%20the%20shoulders.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20it%20lived%20up%20to%20its%20promises%20by%20encouraging%20good%20spinal%20alignment%20and%20reducing%20discomfort%20in%20the%20neck%2C%20shoulders%2C%20and%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20adjustable%20fill%20is%20made%20from%20a%20combination%20of%20natural%20latex%20noodles%20and%20polyester%20fibers%20that%20give%20it%20a%20cooling%20effect.%20It%20also%20includes%20a%20removable%20cover%20made%20from%20smooth%20cotton%2C%20blended%20with%20ultra-fine%20polyester%20and%20spandex.%20All%20materials%20are%20breathable%20and%20prevent%20heat%20retention%20effectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndividuals%20who%20prefer%20traditional%2C%20non-shaped%20pillows%20might%20need%20some%20time%20to%20get%20used%20to%20the%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20pillow%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20recommend%20it%20to%20side%20sleepers%20who%20also%20switch%20to%20sleeping%20on%20their%20stomach%20during%20the%20night%2C%20as%20it%20does%20not%20provide%20adequate%20head%20and%20neck%20support%20in%20that%20position.%20This%20pillow%20is%20on%20the%20pricier%20side%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20a%20worthwhile%20investment.%20Fortunately%2C%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20offers%20a%2045-day%20return%20policy%20so%20you%20can%20try%20it%20before%20committing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20cooling%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222681%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20places%20two%20hands%20on%20the%20Purple%20Harmony%20Pillow%20that's%20resting%20on%20a%20mattress.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6520574c6e038039826c3398%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222011%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Purple%20Harmony%20is%20a%20medium-soft%20pillow%20that%20conforms%20well%20to%20the%20head%20and%20neck%20while%20offering%20solid%20support%20for%20side%20and%20back%20sleepers%20who%20remain%20relatively%20still%20during%20the%20night.%3Cp%3ESuzy%