ates%20hip%20and%20knee%20pressure%2C%20ensuring%20a%20comfortable%20position%20for%20side%20sleepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%2C%20who%20struggles%20with%20sleep%20apnea%2C%20reported%20the%20Puff%20to%20be%20incredibly%20helpful%20in%20maintaining%20proper%20alignment%20on%20his%20head%20and%20neck%2C%20with%20just%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20elevation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20particularly%20like%20that%20the%20pillow%20stays%20cool%20without%20overheating%20and%20is%20made%20with%20high-quality%20materials%2C%20including%20a%20fiber%20that%20mimics%20the%20plushness%20of%20down%20and%20a%20smooth%2C%20silky%20pillowcase.%20It%20held%20its%20shape%20over%20time%20while%20providing%20consistent%20comfort%2C%20proper%20spinal%20alignment%2C%20and%20reliable%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20pillow%20for%20side%20sleepers%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20stuffs%20a%20pillow%20into%20a%20case%20while%20packaging%20sits%20around%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652064a89f7ca8b2bbdc766c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKey%20factors%20to%20consider%20when%20shopping%20for%20a%20side%20sleeper%20pillow%20include%20adjustability%2C%20which%20will%20help%20you%20dial%20in%20the%20pillow's%20loft%20to%20your%20anatomy.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESelecting%20the%20perfect%20pillow%20is%20a%20highly%20individual%20decision%2C%20but%20for%20side%20sleepers%2C%20it's%20crucial%20to%20focus%20on%20key%20factors%20such%20as%20spinal%20alignment%2C%20head%20support%2C%20and%20overall%20comfort%20to%20ensure%20a%20good%20night's%20sleep.%20Here%20are%20the%20primary%20essential%20components%20side%20sleepers%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20when%20choosing%20a%20pillow%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c14d3b3c-184e-46a7-9628-3456c88f986f%5C%22%3ELoft%20and%20adjustability%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESide%20sleepers%20should%20opt%20for%20a%20medium%20to%20high%20loft%20pillow%20to%20properly%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20their%20head%20and%20the%20mattress.%20This%20gap%20will%20differ%20from%20person-to-person%2C%20so%20we%20recommend%20opting%20for%20a%20pillow%20with%20adjustable%20fill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22721dfd81-34ec-40bb-9cd6-12c8d89b6c74%5C%22%3EAlignment%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHayden%20told%20us%20that%20good%20sleeping%20posture%20helps%20prevent%20stress%20points%20that%20may%20aggravate%20joints%20and%20connective%20tissue.%20A%20quality%20pillow%20should%20offer%20excellent%20support%20for%20the%20head%20and%20shoulders%2C%20ensuring%20proper%20spinal%20alignment%20while%20alleviating%20shoulder%20pressure%20without%20excessive%20head%20elevation.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20coach%20my%20patients%20to%20sleep%20on%20their%20side%20with%20a%20body%20pillow%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hayden.%20%26quot%3BThis%20keeps%20the%20spine%20straight%20and%20aligned.%20A%20pillow%20under%20the%20head%20should%20be%20just%20high%20enough%20to%20keep%20the%20head%20level%20with%20the%20mattress.%20The%20upper%20arm%20and%20upper%20knee%20are%20to%20be%20supported%20by%20the%20body%20pillow%20to%20keep%20the%20spine%20straight%20while%20you%20sleep.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b319f5e0-92e7-4b26-a7d6-91ee2a7917bb%5C%22%3EFirmness%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESelecting%20the%20right%20pillow%20firmness%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20preference%2C%20but%20most%20side%20sleepers%20prefer%20a%20medium-firm%20feel%20and%20our%20picks%20reflect%20that.%20Your%20pillow%20should%20be%20firm%20enough%20to%20maintain%20proper%20spinal%20alignment%2C%20but%20not%20so%20firm%20that%20it%20causes%20discomfort%20or%20morning%20headaches.%20A%20good%20pillow%20should%20contour%20comfortably%20to%20the%20head%20and%20neck.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22875734f0-4d04-436d-89eb-27a6f7fa9665%5C%22%3EMaterials%2Ffill%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20pillow%20fill%20and%20materials%20can%20impact%20support%2C%20comfort%2C%20breathability%2C%20and%20maintenance.%20Some%20fills%20are%20hypoallergenic%2C%20offer%20improved%20breathability%2C%20and%20varying%20levels%20of%20support.%20When%20opting%20for%20foam%20fill%2C%20check%20that%20it's%20CertiPUR-US%20certified%20for%20quality%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a2856bb-2e8c-407b-b315-451c67a5df1d%5C%22%3ETemperature%20regulation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESide%20sleepers%20who%20get%20hot%20during%20the%20night%20should%20opt%20for%20a%20breathable%20pillow%20designed%20to%20regulate%20temperature.%20Some%20pillows%20even%20feature%20advanced%20technologies%20to%20effectively%20dissipate%20body%20heat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224169dd4f-1c21-4abf-aad5-aa12127086d7%5C%22%3EReturn%20policy%2Ftrial%20period%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20recommend%20only%20considering%20pillows%20that%20allow%20you%20to%20return%20the%20product%20if%20you%20find%20it's%20not%20for%20you.%20Side%20sleepers%20may%20need%20to%20try%20multiple%20options%20to%20find%20the%20perfect%20fit%2C%20and%20you%20should%20give%20yourself%20at%20least%20a%20week%20to%20adjust%20to%20sleeping%20on%20a%20new%20pillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20test%20pillows%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20hands%20placing%20a%20pillow%20into%20a%20washing%20machine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652063d36e038039826c5031%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20washed%20and%20dried%20every%20pillow%20to%20see%20how%20it%20retained%20its%20shape%20as%20part%20of%20testing%20for%20the%20best%20pillows%20for%20side%20sleepers.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20certified%20sleep%20science%20consultant%20with%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20sleep%20research%20and%20product%20reviews%2C%20I%20know%20first%20hand%20the%20significance%20of%20a%20well-equipped%20bedroom%20for%20a%20comfortable%20and%20healthy%20night's%20sleep.%20To%20delve%20deeper%20into%20what%20makes%20the%20best%20pillow%20for%20side%20sleepers%2C%20we%20consulted%20experts%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iriscitychiropractic.com%2Four-team%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobert%20Hayden%2C%20DC%2C%20PhD%3C%2Fa%3E%20founder%20of%20the%20The%20Iris%20City%20Chiropractic%20Center%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fintrabalance.com%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENishi%20Bhopal%2C%20MD%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20board%20certified%20psychiatrist%20and%20sleep%20specialist.%20Using%20their%20recommendations%2C%20I%20conducted%20a%20comprehensive%20assessment%20by%20testing%20more%20than%2020%20of%20the%20best%20pillows%20on%20the%20market%2C%20evaluating%20the%20following%20key%20factors%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESleeping%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20slept%20on%20each%20pillow%20for%20seven%20consecutive%20nights%2C%20assessing%20factors%20like%20sleep%20quality%2C%20comfort%2C%20temperature%20regulation%2C%20support%2C%20and%20spinal%20alignment%20to%20provide%20insights%20on%20each%20pillow.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%20and%20certifications%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20noted%20each%20pillow's%20materials%2C%20looking%20for%20qualities%20like%20hypoallergenic%20properties%2C%20breathability%2C%20certifications%20(such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcertipur.us%2Fabout-the-seal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECertiPUR-US%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20and%20maintenance%20requirements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPillows%20inevitably%20accumulate%20body%20oils%2C%20sweat%2C%20and%20dead%20skin%2C%20so%20cleaning%20is%20crucial%20to%20proper%20sleep%20hygiene.%20I%20followed%20cleaning%20instructions%20for%20each%20pillow%20and%20assessed%20washing%20and%20drying%20difficulty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EShape%20retention%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20examined%20each%20pillow%20for%20lumps%20or%20clumping%20after%20use%2C%20noting%20how%20often%20they%20required%20fluffing%20and%20whether%20they%20maintained%20their%20shape%20and%20loft.%20This%20is%20particularly%20important%20for%20side-sleepers%20who%20rely%20on%20consistent%20support.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturn%20policy%2Ftrial%20period%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20also%20investigated%20the%20return%20policy%20and%20warranty%20for%20each%20pillow%2C%20as%20no%20single%20pillow%20suit's%20everyone%20needs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESide%20sleeper%20pillow%20FAQs%3Ch3%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20pillow%20should%20side%20sleepers%20use%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Nishi%20and%20Hayden%2C%20side%20sleepers%20should%20opt%20for%20a%20pillow%20that%20supports%20the%20head%2C%20neck%20and%20spine%20alignment%20which%20will%20help%20prevent%20stress%20points%20that%20may%20aggravate%20joints%C2%A0and%20connective%20tissue.%20Hayden%20also%20suggests%20placing%20a%20pillow%20between%20the%20knees%20to%20help%20maintain%20a%20neutral%20spine%20position.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EShould%20a%20side%20sleeper%20have%20a%20soft%20or%20hard%20pillow%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESide%20sleepers%20should%20use%20a%20pillow%20that%20is%20on%20the%20firmer%20side.%20Generally%20a%20medium-firm%20or%20firm%20pillow%20is%20best%2C%20said%20Nishi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EDo%20side%20sleepers%20need%20thicker%20pillows%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENishi%20does%20not%20recommend%20pillows%20that%20are%20too%20thick%20or%20tall%20because%20they%20can%20tilt%20the%20head%20out%20of%20alignment%20with%20the%20spine.%20The%20pillow%20should%20be%20thick%20enough%20to%20fill%20the%20space%20between%20the%20head%20and%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EWhat%20type%20of%20pillow%20is%20best%20for%20side%20sleepers%20with%20shoulder%20pain%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20U-shaped%20design%20can%20help%20take%20some%20of%20the%20pressure%20off%20the%20neck%20and%20shoulders%20while%20keeping%20the%20spine%20aligned%2C%20says%20Nishi.%20Additionally%2C%20Hayden%20recommends%20choosing%20a%20pillow%20that%20supports%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20shoulder%20and%20head.%20If%20the%20pillow%20is%20too%20thin%2C%20your%20head%20and%20shoulder%20are%20crunched%20together.%20If%20the%20pillow%20is%20too%20thick%2C%20your%20head%20is%20bumped%20up%2C%20straining%20the%20alignment%20of%20your%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillow-for-side-sleepers%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729803275000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652055496561dd877e738510%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillow-for-side-sleepers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20had%20a%20certified%20sleep%20coach%20test%2020%20different%20pillows%20to%20find%20the%20best%20for%20side%20sleepers.%20Our%20picks%20include%20down%2C%20shredded%20memory%20foam%2C%20and%20latex.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Suzy%20Hernandez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillow-for-side-sleepers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Stealth%20version%20of%20the%20far%20left'%3A%20Comedian%20Bill%20Maher%20advises%20Kamala%20Harris%20against%20posing%20herself%20as%20'woke%20President'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729803066000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114559978%2Cimgsize-1168233.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus