the%20United%20States.%20If%20they%20are%20open%2C%20then%20we%20will%20also%20be%20open.%20And%20if%20they%20don't%20want%20it%2C%20then%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20told%20reporters%20in%20Kazan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20the%20two%20superpowers%20have%20sunk%20to%20their%20lowest%20since%20the%20Cold%20War%20amid%20Moscow's%20military%20offensive%20on%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20month's%20US%20election%20is%20set%20to%20be%20critical%20to%20the%20course%20of%20future%20ties%20and%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20expressed%20scepticism%20over%20Washington's%20multi-billion%20dollar%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20claimed%20that%20if%20elected%20he%20could%20end%20the%20fighting%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20said%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bspoke%20about%20his%20desire%20to%20do%20everything%20to%20end%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine.%20I%20think%20he%20is%20being%20sincere.%20Of%20course%20we%20welcome%20statements%20like%20this%2C%20whoever%20they%20come%20from.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EREALITIES%20ON%20GROUND%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20were%20among%20around%2020%20leaders%20that%20gathered%20for%20the%20BRICS%20summit%2C%20the%20largest%20diplomatic%20event%20in%20Russia%20since%20Putin%20ordered%20troops%20into%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin%20leader%20said%20Moscow%20was%20open%20to%20considering%20peace%20initiatives%20and%20welcomed%20BRICS%20leaders%20offering%20to%20mediate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%20any%20deal%20must%20consider%20the%20%26quot%3Brealities%20on%20the%20ground%26quot%3B%20--%20a%20reference%20to%20Ukrainian%20territory%20controlled%20by%20Russian%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20to%20look%20at%20any%20proposals%20for%20peace%20negotiations%20that%20are%20based%2