3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20I%20increased%20the%20risk%20factor%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%3Eretirement%20savings%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20second%20year%20in%20a%20row.%20I%20made%20this%20change%20because%20my%20time%20horizon%20for%20using%20these%20funds%20is%20long.%20In%20a%20sense%2C%20I'm%20dipping%20my%20toes%20into%20slightly%20more%20aggressive%20investments%20as%20a%20form%20of%20exposure%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20thing%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20risk%20tolerance%2C%20Liz%20told%20me%20%E2%80%94%20setting%20aside%20the%20emotional%2C%20psychological%20part%20%E2%80%94%20is%20your%20timeline%20for%20using%20this%20money%20and%20how%20rigid%20that%20timeline%20is.%20The%20shorter%20your%20timeline%2C%20the%20less%20risk%20you'll%20want%20to%20take%20on%20with%20your%20investments.%20%26quot%3BThe%20longer%20or%20more%20flexible%20your%20timeline%2C%20the%20more%20risk%20you%20can%20generally%20afford%20to%20take%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20long-term%20investments%20(over%2025%20years)%2C%20the%20performance%20of%20comparable%20conservative%20and%20aggressive%20portfolios%20is%20very%20small.%20They%20can%20look%20very%20different%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20but%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20things%20tend%20to%20average%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20risk%20factor%20matters%20most%20when%20your%20timeline%20is%20short%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you're%20planning%20on%20using%20that%20money%20soon.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20be%20really%20conscious%20of%20how%20much%20risk%20you%20can%20afford%20to%20take%20if%20you're%20planning%20on%20using%20that%20money%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Liz%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20if%20your%20timeline%20is%20long%2C%20it%20actually%20matters%20less%20than%20you%20might%20think%2C%20whether%20you%20invest%20really%20aggressively%20or%20really%20conservatively%20%E2%80%94%2