id%20she%20wants%20as%20many%20new%20fans%20for%20the%20Liberty%20and%20WNBA%20as%20possible%2C%20but%20not%20if%20they%20have%20bad%20attitudes%20about%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20heard%20male%20fans%20online%20say%2C%20'You%20should%20be%20grateful%20to%20Caitlin%20Clark%20that%20we're%20even%20watching%20this%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20actually%20want%20you%20to%20watch%20it%20then%2C%20because%20you're%20not%20appreciating%20all%20the%20other%20players.%20She's%20good%2C%20but%20there%20are%20so%20many%20amazing%20players.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECollege%20basketball%20players%20In%C3%A9s%20Gimenez%2C%2022%2C%20and%20Nitzan%20Amar%2C%2023%2C%20are%20ecstatic%20about%20the%20future%20of%20their%20sport.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%C3%A9s%20Gimenez%20and%20Nitzan%20Amar%20pose%20together%20on%20the%20New%20York%20City%20sidewalk%20of%20the%20championship%20parade.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a70a29b3250dbbce9c75d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%C3%A9s%20Gimenez%2C%20left%2C%20and%20Nitzan%20Amar%2C%20right.%3Cp%3EDan%20Latu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20basketball%20teammates%20at%20Manhattan%20University%20in%20the%20Bronx%20came%20to%20the%20parade%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20they%20might%20be%20the%20players%20on%20the%20floats%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20both%20finish%20college%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Amar%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20plan%20is%20to%20go%20pro%20next%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGimenez%2C%20from%20Spain%2C%20and%20Amar%2C%20from%20Israel%2C%20said%20watching%20the%20explosion%20of%20support%20for%20women's%20basketball%20in%20New%20York%20City%20and%20the%20United%20States%20has%20been%20exhilarating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20friends%20that%20said%20they%20would%20never%20watch%20a%20WNBA%20game%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now%20they're%20superfans%2C%26quot%3B%20Gimenez%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20overwhelming.%20We%20deserve%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGimenez%20attended%20the%20championship%20final%20on%20Sunday%20at%20the%20Barclays%20Center%20in%20Brooklyn%20and%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20electric%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20never%20seen%20a%20women's%2C%20or%20even%20a%20men's%2C%20basketball%20game%20with%20that%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Gimenez%20said.%20%26quot%3BSeeing%20that%20as%20a%20player%2C%20it's%20just%20crazy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-liberty-wnba-championship-parade-photos-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729800537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a8b649b3250dbbce9d752%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-liberty-wnba-championship-parade-photos-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20New%20York%20Liberty%20celebrated%20their%20WNBA%20championship%20win%20with%20a%20parade%20through%20New%20York%20City's%20Financial%20District.%20See%20photos.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmaniece%40businessinsider.com%20(Mykenna%20Maniece%2CDan%20Latu)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A61%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-liberty-wnba-championship-parade-photos-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Annu%20Kapoor%20dissatisfied%20over%20SRK's%20Chak%20De!%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729800430000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114559680%2Cimgsize-18826.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fannu-kapoor-expresses-dissatisf