%2Ftypes%2Fcolon-rectal-cancer%2Fdetection-diagnosis-staging%2Facs-recommendations.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Cancer%20Society%3C%2Fa%3E%20recommends%20adults%20with%20an%20average%20risk%20for%20colorectal%20cancer%20begin%20having%20regular%20colonoscopies%20at%2045.%20I%20had%20my%20first%20colonoscopy%20when%20I%20was%20only%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-travel-constipation-stay-regular-dietitian-packng-list-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggled%20with%20constipation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20bleeding%20with%20bowel%20movements%20since%20childhood.%20I%20would%20have%20a%20bowel%20movement%20maybe%20once%20a%20week%2C%20growing%20up.%20At%20primary%20care%20checkups%2C%20doctors%20would%20tell%20my%20parents%2C%20%26quot%3BGive%20her%20Metamucil%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20supplements.%20My%20parents%20said%20they'd%20try%20things%20but%20never%20changed%20my%20diet.%20My%20parents%20both%20worked%20and%20had%20other%20priorities%20to%20manage.%20Growing%20up%2C%20my%20diet%20consisted%20of%20highly%20processed%20foods%2C%20like%20fast%20foods%2C%20and%20a%20high-fat%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%2016%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20become%20vegan%2C%20but%20I%20was%20still%20eating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplant-based-upf-processed-linked-heart-disease-death-study-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-processed%20vegan%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20the%20change%20didn't%20help%20my%20digestive%20issues.%20Even%20at%205'9%20and%20living%20an%20active%20lifestyle%2C%20I%20did%20not%20use%20the%20restroom%20regularly.%20Feeling%20sluggish%20and%20bloated%20felt%20normal%20to%20me.%20The%20bleeding%20with%20bowel%20movements%20continued%20on%20and%20off%20through%20adulthood%20but%20got%20continuously%20worse%20with%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c13b8148-5e3f-4c37-8b9a-ac83bce9526f%5C%22%3EI%20wa