islature%20Party%20leader%20Balasaheb%20Thorat%20from%20Sangamner%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Vijay%20Wadettiwar%20from%20Bramhapuri%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20from%20Karad%20South%20and%20CWC%20Member%20and%20Regional%20Working%20President%20Naseem%20Khan%20from%20Chandivali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20locked%20into%20some%20tough%20bargaining%20with%20ally%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20for%20weeks%2C%20confident%20that%20it%20would%20manage%20the%20maximum%20victories%20after%20its%20vastly%20improved%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20had%20been%20demanding%20125%20of%20the%20state's%20288%20assembly%20seats%2C%20while%20Sena%20had%20its%20counter-offer%20of%20%C2%A0100%20seats.%20The%20Sena%20also%20wanted%20100%20seats%C2%A0%20and%20had%20suggested%20that%2088%20seats%20be%20left%20for%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20time%20running%20out%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20had%20intervened%20and%20after%20multiple%20sessions%20of%20discussions%20with%20both%20partners%2C%20had%20devised%20the%2085-85-85%20formula.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20have%20said%20they%20would%20offer%20the%20rest%20to%20smaller%20partners%20and%20if%20there's%20any%20seat%20left%2C%20would%20divide%20it%20up%20between%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)'s%20Sanjay%20Raut%20said%20a%20consensus%20has%20been%20reached%20on%20270%20of%20the%20288%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20include%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20PWP%2C%20CPI(M)%2C%20CPI%20and%20AAP.%20Discussions%20are%20still%20on%20for%20the%20remaining%20seats.%20We%20have%20amicably%20arrived%20at%20a%20consensus%20on%20270%20seats.%20The%20MVA%20stands%20united%20to%20defeat%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raut%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20for%20the%20288-member%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20will%20be%20held%20on%20November%2020%2C%20and%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20November%2023.%20The%20term%20of%20the%20current%20assembly%20will%20end%20on%20November%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729788780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F6p0qlnto_maharashtra-congress_625x300_08_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-announces-first-list-of-45-candidates-for-maharashtra-election-6865893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20announced%20its%20first%20list%20of%2048%20candidates%20for%20the%20coming%20Maharashtra%20election%20this%20evening%20-%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20announced%2085-85-85%20seat%20share%20formula.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-announces-first-list-of-45-candidates-for-maharashtra-election-6865893%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BToo%20Much%20Immigration%26quot%3B%3A%20Canada%20Slashes%20Immigrant%20Intake%20Amid%20Public%20Worry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanada%20said%20Thursday%20it%20was%20significantly%20curbing%20immigration%20targets%2C%20a%20dramatic%20shift%20that%20comes%20as%20public%20support%20for%20new%20arrivals%20declines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20a%20big%20pivot%20for%20a%20country%20with%20a%20long-standing%20reputation%20as%20a%20destination%20for%20immigrants%2C%20including%20economic%20migrants%20from%20the%20developing%20world%20seeking%20better%20living%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada's%20population%20jumped%203.2%20percent%20from%202023%20to%202024%2C%20the%20biggest%20annual%20rise%20since%201957%2C%20and%20now%20stands%20at%2041%20million%2C%20the%20national%20statistic%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20rise%20was%20partly%20fuelled%20by%20an%20unprecedented%20wave%20of%20new%20arrivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20curbs%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20said%20the%20influx%20helped%20the%20Canadian%20economy%20bounce%20back%20from%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20but%20the%20time%20had%20come%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Badjustments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20we're%20announcing%20that%20we%20will%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20immigrants%20we%20bring%20in%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20which%20will%20result%20in%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20population%20growth%20over%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20said%20Canada%20needed%20to%20stabilize%20its%20population%20to%20give%20%26quot%3Ball%20levels%20of%20government%20time%20to%20catch%20up%2C%20time%20to%20make%20the%20necessary%20investments%20in%20health%20care%2C%20in%20housing%2C%20(and)%20in%20social%20services%20to%20accommodate%20more%20people%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immigration%20ministry%20had%20previously%20planned%20to%20let%20500%2C000%20new%20permanent%20residents%20settle%20in%20the%20country%20in%202025%20and%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20new%20targets%20were%20revised%20down%20to%20395%2C000%20next%20year%20and%20380%2C000%20for%202026.%20It%20set%20the%202027%20target%20at%20365%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmigration%20Minister%20Marc%20Miller%20called%20the%20plan%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20broad%20efforts%20to%20control%20population%20growth%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20last%20census%20in%202021%2C%2023%20percent%20of%20the%20population%20was%20foreign-born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatistic%20Canada%20said%20that%20as%20of%202021%20most%20immigrants%20were%20from%20Asia%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20but%20an%20increasing%20share%20were%20coming%20from%20Africa.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20one%20of%20five%20recent%20immigrants%20were%20born%20in%20India%2C%20the%20statistics%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EANTI-IMMIGRANT%20SENTIMENT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20last%20month%20from%20the%20Environics%20Institute%20on%20public%20attitudes%20toward%20immigration%20found%20that%20%26quot%3Bfor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20quarter%20century%2C%20a%20clear%20majority%20of%20Canadians%20say%20there%20is%20too%20much%20immigration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty-eight%20percent%20of%20Canadians%20believe%20the%20country%20takes%20in%20too%20many%20immigrants%2C%20up%2014%20percentage%20points%20from%202023%2C%20the%20survey%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20figures%20released%20last%20week%2C%20Abacus%20Data%20found%20that%20one%20of%20every%20two%20Canadians%20say%20immigration%20is%20harming%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Abacus%20figures%20also%20noted%20that%20concern%20among%20Canadians%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20immigration%20is%20mostly%20linked%20to%20unease%20regarding%20a%20perceived%20lack%20of%20essential%20resources%2C%20notably%20affordable%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiller%20in%20particular%20stressed%20the%20new%20plans%20efforts%20to%20address%20what%20many%20Canadians%20refer%20to%20as%20a%20housing%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20predicted%20that%20revising%20immigration%20targets%20downwards%20will%20address%20the%20housing%20supply%20gap%2C%20reducing%20by%20670%2C000%20the%20number%20of%20homes%20Canada%20needs%20to%20build%20by%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20told%20reporters.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%