C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20Instagram%20post%2C%20Mr%20Shetty%20shared%20his%20experience%20working%20with%20the%20world's%20wealthiest%20man.%20He%20described%20Musk's%20demanding%20leadership%20style%20and%20the%20surprising%20ways%20he%20made%20employees%20feel%20valued.%20Mr%20Musk's%20passion%20for%20sustainability%20and%20his%20visionary%20leadership%20were%20evident%2C%20making%20him%20not%20just%20a%20boss%2C%20but%20a%20leader%20who%20changed%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20joined%20Tesla%20when%20it%20was%20Tesla%20Motors%20and%20there%20were%20only%20a%20few%20people.%20Which%20meant%20we%20got%20the%20hands%20on%20experience%20and%20front%20seat%20tickets%20to%20how%20Elon%20Musk%20turned%20his%20company%20into%20what%20it%20is%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20shared%20in%20his%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20listed%20down%20a%20few%20things%20that%20one%20can%20learn%20from%20Elon%20Musk.%20Mr%20Shetty%20reflected%20on%20Mr%20Musk's%20leadership%20style.%20He%20highlighted%2C%20%26quot%3BHis%20no%20bullshit%20attitude-%20Now%20before%20you%20go%20on%20saying%20this%20is%20not%20right%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time%20and%20especially%20when%20you're%20the%20boss%2C%20you%20need%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20nonsense%20and%20talk%20openly.%20It%20reduces%20any%20chances%20of%20miscommunication%2C%20secrets%20and%20disrespect.%20Elon%20made%20sure%20to%20address%20everyone%20through%20his%20emails%20and%20went%20straight%20to%20the%20point.%20He%20knew%20his%20time%20and%20his%20employees's%20time%20was%20precious%20and%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20waste%20any%20of%20it%20with%20unnecessary%20distractions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20second%20point%2C%20he%20emphasised%20that%20Mr%20Musk's%20support%20and%20appreciation%20for%20his%20employees%20was%20unparalleled.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20my%20time%20at%20Tesla%2C%20Elon%20did%20not%20make%20any%20one%20employee%20feel%20unappreciated.%20I%20still%20remember%20his%20mails%20used%20to%20come%20at%20odd%20hours%20in%20the%20night%20just%20expressing%20how%20thankful%20he%20was%20for%20the%20team%20and%20how%20he's%20proud%20of%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20us.%20Call%20him%20what%20you%20want%20to%20but%20the%20guy%20cherished%20his%20employees%20and%20made%20them%20feel%20worthwhile%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shetty%20also%20talked%20about%20Mr%20Musk's%20ambition%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20I%20remember%20clearly%20about%20Elon%20is%20his%20ambition.%20The%20guy%20worked%20nonstop%20and%20always%20strived%20for%20more.%20It's%20this%20passion%20and%20ambition%20for%20the%20work%20they%20are%20doing%20which%20makes%20you%20a%20visionary.%20And%20Elon%20was%20definitely%20a%20visionary.%20Even%20when%20Tesla%20was%20Tesla%20Motors%2C%20Elon%20constantly%20had%20ideas%20to%20push%20his%20motive%20of%20sustainability%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20concluded%20his%20post%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BLove%20or%20hate%20the%20guy%2C%20you%20have%20to%20admit%20he's%20doing%20something%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDAWwdqPMrIJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDAWwdqPMrIJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDAWwdqPMrIJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView