%20Great's%20Big%20Advice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMayank%20Yadav%20should%20be%20on%20the%20plane%20to%20Australia%20if%20Mohammed%20Shami%20is%20not%20available%20for%20selection%2C%20asserted%20Brett%20Lee%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20devastatingly%20destructive%20bowlers%2C%20who%20has%20high%20hopes%20from%20the%20Indian%20pace%20sensation%20on%20the%20true%2C%20bouncy%20wickets%20Down%20Under.%20Aiming%20to%20qualify%20for%20a%20third%20successive%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20final%2C%20India%20will%20be%20travelling%20to%20Australia%20next%20month%20to%20defend%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20and%20doubts%20remain%20over%20seasoned%20seamer%20Shami's%20selection%20in%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20five-match%20Test%20series.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20batters%20are%20okay%20when%20you%20bowl%20that%20135-140%20kmph%20speed%2C%20but%20when%20you%20bowl%20high%20150s%2C%20I%20don't%20care%20who%20it%20is%2C%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20face%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20looks%20like%20someone%20who%20is%20a%20complete%20package%2C%20if%20Mohammed%20Shami%20is%20not%20ready%2C%20at%20least%20get%20him%20(Mayank)%20in%20the%20squad.%20I%20think%20he%20would%20do%20pretty%20well%20on%20these%20Australian%20wickets%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20told%20Fox%20Cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%20has%20not%20played%20since%20featuring%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20last%20November%2C%20and%20even%20though%20he%20went%20full%20tilt%20at%20the%20nets%20recently%2C%20India%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20is%20averse%20to%20taking%20an%20%26quot%3Bundercooked%26quot%3B%20version%20of%20the%20seamer%20to%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Aussie%20pacer%20Lee%20knows%20a%20thing%20or%20two%20about%20batters'%20discomfort%20while%20standing%20up%20to%20express%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20great%20thing%20is%20with%20me%20that%20I%20get%20to%20work%20on%20the%20IPL%20and%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20young%20Indian%20cricketers.%20Mayank%20Yadav%2C%20to%20watch%20his%20first%20IPL%20game%20recently%2C%20hit%20157%20kmph%20first%20up%20in%20his%20first%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20his%20franchise%20probably%20brought%20him%20a%20little%20early%20and%20he%20did%20his%20side%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20put%20him%20in%20cotton%20wool%20for%20a%20bit.%20The%20great%20thing%20about%20India%20is%20that%20they%20are%20not%20worried%20about%20how%20much%20cricket%20someone%20has%20played%20or%20hasn't%20played%2C%20if%20he%20is%20ready%20to%20go%2C%20get%20him%20in%20there.%20I%20actually%20love%20that%20theory%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20boast%20of%20a%20world-class%20bowling%20attack%20that%20can%20trouble%20the%20Australian%20batters%20in%20their%20own%20den%2C%20and%20Lee%20acknowledged%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAshwin%20is%20approaching%20600%20wickets%2C%20he%20has%20got%20that%20beautiful%20shape%20when%20he%20bowls%20spin.%20He%20can%20bowl%20with%20the%20new%20ball%20as%20well%20but%20I%20think%20if%20India%20have%20to%20win%20there%2C%20then%20Shami%20(provided%20he%20is%20fit)%20can%20definitely%20hold%20the%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20we%20all%20know%20how%20good%20he%20is%2C%20he%20can%20bowl%20both%20ways%2C%20he%20is%20a%20great%20exponent%20of%20reverse%20swing.%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20knows%20how%20to%20make%20the%20new%20ball%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20wickets%20like%20Perth%2C%20Adelaide%2C%20for%20me%20it's%20the%20combination%2C%20these%20three%20fast%20bowlers%20with%20Ashwin%20as%20the%20spinner.%20Then%20they%20have%20got%20options%20with%20guys%20like%20who%20are%20part-time%20spinners.%20But%20you%20need%20to%20have%20those%20three%20quicks%20firing%20if%20India%20wants%20to%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'India%20don't%20want%20to%20bow%20down'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee%20described%20the%20Indian%20team%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpowerhouse%20that%20don't%20want%20to%20bow%20down%26quot%3B%20to%20anyone%2C%20cautioning%20his%20compatriots%20who%20will%20take%20on%20the%20Asian%20giants%20from%20November%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee's%20remarks%20came%20after%20India's%20eight-wicket%20defeat%20to%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%20Bengaluru%20Test%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20day%20and%20age%2C%20India%20is%20a%20powerhouse%20that%20don't%20want%20to%20bow%20down.%20They%20know%20how%20to%20win%2C%20and%20they%20know%20they%20can%20beat%20Australia%3B%20they%20know%20they%20can%20beat%20the%20Kiwis.%20They%20know%20they%20can%20beat%20anyone%20on%20any%20given%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20India's%20outing%20in%20the%20Bengaluru%20Test%20against%20the%20Kiwis%2C%20Lee%20felt%20that%20they%20might%20have%20got%20influenced%20by%20'Bazball'%2C%20leading%20to%20playing%20some%20loose%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20just%20didn't%20go%20into%20their%20shell.%20Maybe%20it's%20Bazball%20brushing%20off%20on%20other%20cricketers%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20India%20won't%20be%20proud%20of%20the%20way%20they%20played.%20They%20played%20some%20pretty%20loose%20shots.%26quot%3B%20India's%20decision%20to%20bat%20first%20in%20overcast%20conditions%20raised%20eyebrows%2C%20as%20the%20team%20was%20bowled%20out%20for%2046%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20of%20the%20opening%20Test%2C%20its%20lowest%20Test%20score%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee%20said%20the%20side%20needs%20to%20%26quot%3Bweigh%20up%20the%20risk%20factor%26quot%3B%20and%20added%20the%20Indians%20should%20have%20judged%20the%20conditions%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20you've%20got%20to%20weigh%20up%20the%20risk%20factor%20as%20well.%20There%20are%20times%20when%20you've%20got%20to%20go%2C%20