%20Speaking%20to%20PTI%20on%20Thursday%2C%20he%20highlighted%20alarming%20living%20conditions%20and%20academic%20environments%20faced%20by%20these%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20our%20children%20are%20not%20getting%20what%20they%20dreamed%20of.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20eight%20students%20are%20sharing%20one%20room%20for%20accommodation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Verma%20said.%20He%20further%20elaborated%20on%20the%20academic%20challenges%2C%20revealing%20that%20some%20students%20attend%20colleges%20where%20classes%20are%20held%20just%20once%20a%20week.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20week%2C%20they%20are%20forced%20to%20work%20as%20daily%20wage%20earners%20in%20stores%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20emphasising%20that%20these%20students%20come%20from%20good%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20envoy%20noted%20that%20despite%20their%20higher%20education%2C%20many%20students%20are%20resorting%20to%20low-paying%20jobs%2C%20often%20working%20as%20cab%20drivers%20or%20in%20other%20menial%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Verma's%20comments%20come%20in%20response%20to%20growing%20concerns%20from%20parents%20sending%20their%20children%20abroad%20for%20higher%20education%2C%20hoping%20for%20better%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20students%20in%20Canada%20%26quot%3Bshould%20be%20aware%20of%20their%20surroundings%26quot%3B%20and%20resist%20radicalisation%20attempts%20by%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%2C%20Sanjay%20Verma%20told%20NDTV%20on%20Thursday%20evening.%20He%20urged%20the%20parents%20of%20students%20in%20Canada%20to%20%26quot%3Bplease%20talk%20to%20them%20regularly%20and%20try%20to%20understand%26quot%3B%20their%20situation%2C%20and%20to%20guide%20them%20away%20from%20unwise%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20time%20in%20Canada%2C%20there%20is%20a%20threat%20from%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%20to%20the%20larger%20Indian%20community%2C%20including%20students%20(of%20whom%20there%20were%20around%20319%2C000%20as%20of%202023)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20this%20(Khalistani%20terrorists'%20outreach%20to%20Indian%20students%20in%20Canada)%20works%20is%20that%2C%20given%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20there%20are%20few%20jobs.%20Students%20are%20offered%20money%20and%20food%2C%20and%20this%20is%20how%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%20influence%20them%20with%20nefarious%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Verma%20explained%20to%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20students%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20also%20persuaded%20to%20take%20photographs%20or%20videos%20of%20themselves%20'protesting'-shouting%20anti-India%20slogans%20or%20insulting%20the%20flag%20outside%20Indian%20diplomatic%20buildings%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20they%20are%20told%20to%20seek%20asylum%2C%20with%20the%20justification%20being%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20go%20back%20to%20India%20now%2C%20I%20will%20be%20punished.'%20There%20have%20been%20cases%20of%20such%20students%20being%20granted%20asylum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729781820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fkdsg721_indias-recalled-high-commissioner-to-canada-sanjay-verma_625x300_24_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Findian-students-resort-to-working-as-daily-wagers-cab-drivers-in-canada-indian-envoy-6865367%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20envoy%20noted%20that%20despite%20their%20higher%20education%2C%20many%20students%20are%20resorting%20to%20low-paying%20jobs%2C%20often%20working%20as%20cab%20drivers%20or%20in%20other%20menial%20positions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Findian-students-resort-to-working-as-daily-wagers-cab-drivers-in-canada-indian-envoy-6865367%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trai's%20new%20traceabili