0-%20may%20enter%20the%20list.%20The%20IPL-winning%20captain%20is%20neither%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20a%20video%20discussion%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fcricket-videos%2Fipl-2025-should-kkr-retain-shreyas-iyer-1456724%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EESPN%20Cricinfo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20an%20'open%20secret'%20that%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders'%20IPL%20-winning%20skipper%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20is%20not%20confirmed%20to%20move%20out%20but%20is%20thinking%20hard%20after%20receiving%20a%20mega%20offer%20from%20a%20rival%20franchise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%2010%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20are%20set%20to%20finalise%20their%20list%20of%20player%20retentions.%20Reports%20have%20claimed%20that%20October%2031st%20is%20the%20last%20day%20to%20submit%20the%20players%20retention%20list%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPL%202025%20mega%20auction.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20is%20planning%20to%20host%20the%20IPL%20mega%20auction%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20November.%20However%2C%20the%20BCCI%20is%20yet%20to%20make%20a%20formal%20announcement%2C%20as%20far%20as%20the%20date%20and%20venue%20are%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20two%20contradictory%20reports%20regarding%20the%20date%20and%20venue%20of%20the%20auction%20have%20emerged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Times%20of%20India%20(TOI)%20reported%20that%20the%20auction%20will%20take%20place%20on%20November%2030.%20The%20IPL%202024%20auction%20was%20held%20in%20Dubai%20last%20year%2C%20and%20the%20report%20claims%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20board%20hosting%20it%20in%20Dubai%26quot%3B%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20Sportstar%20have%20reported%20that%20the%20auction%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Riyadh%20(Saudi%20Arabia)%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20a%20two-day%20affair%20(November%2024%20and%2025).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20London%20and%20Singapore%20were%20considered%20as%20venues%20to%20host%20the%20auction.%20However%2C%20Riyadh%20is%20now%20leading%20the%20race%20because%20of%20a%20favourable%20time%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Board%20and%20the%20IPL%20officials%20are%20in%20the%20'final%20stages'%20of%20finalising%20the%20venue%20that%20can%20accommodate%20the%20entire%20entourage%20-%20including%20delegations%20from%20the%2010%20franchises%20and%20a%20large%20crew%20from%20Jio%20and%20Disney%20Star%20-%20over%20three%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Sportstar%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729780260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F603i8epg_ipl-2024-captains_625x300_24_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fshocking-ipl-move-on-cards-report-claims-ipl-winning-captain-shreyas-iyer-tempted-to-move-out-after-massive-offer-6865158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whenever%20an%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20regular%20enters%20the%20auction%20pool%2C%20it%20throws%20up%20huge%20possibility%20in%20the%20auction%20market%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fshocking-ipl-mo