ada)%20works%20is...%20given%20the%20condition%20of%20that%20economy%20there%20are%20few%20jobs...%20so%20students%20are%20offered%20money%20and%20food%2C%20and%20this%20is%20how%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%20influence%20them%20with%20nefarious%20plans%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Verma%20explained%20to%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20students%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20also%20persuaded%20to%20take%20photographs%20or%20videos%20of%20themselves%20'protesting'%20-%20shouting%20anti-India%20slogans%20or%20insulting%20the%20flag%20-%20outside%20Indian%20diplomatic%20buildings%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20they%20are%20told%20to%20go%20seek%20asylum...%20because%20their%20version%20will%20be%2C%20'If%20I%20go%20back%20to%20India%20now%2C%20I%20will%20be%20punished...'%20and%20there%20have%20been%20cases%20of%20such%20students%20being%20given%20asylum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2C%20therefore%2C%20various%20kinds%20of%20negative%20influences%20acting%20on%20Indian%20students%20in%20Canada%20that%20are%20pushing%20them%20towards%20the%20wrong%20direction%2C%20Mr%20Verma%20told%20NDTV%2C%20as%20he%20appealed%20to%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Verma's%20comments%20come%20as%20the%20India-Canada%20diplomatic%20relationship%20spirals%20downward%20over%20repeated%20and%20unsubstantiated%20claims%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20-%20that%20%26quot%3Bagents%26quot%3B%20of%20Delhi%20conspire%20with%20criminal%20gangs%2C%20including%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20outfit%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Btarget%20(the)%20South%20Asians%26quot%3B%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-bishnoi-gang-canada-bishnoi-gang-linked-to-indian-government-agents-canada-cops-big-claim-6792233%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBishnoi%20Gang%20Linked%20To%20Indian%20Govt%20Agents%26quot