e%20%3Cem%3Ejhuggi-jhopdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2021%2C%20Rahim%E2%80%99s%20life%20tells%20a%20different%20story.%20He%E2%80%99s%20running%20a%20successful%20aquarium%20cleaning%20business%20and%20is%20pursuing%20paramedic%20and%20lab%20technician%20courses.%20He%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20learning%20how%20to%20invest%3B%20he%20is%20also%20sending%20money%20home%20to%20support%20his%20ageing%20mother%20and%20sister.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20even%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359592%2Flinkedin-for-blue-collar-daily-wager-labourer-digital-labour-chowk-job-search-migrant-workers-bihar-uttar-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20providing%20jobs%20to%20others%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20same%20programme%20that%20helped%20him.%20Rahim%20is%20one%20of%20175%20youth%20whose%20lives%20have%20been%20transformed%20by%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EWeLive%20Foundation%2C%20an%20aftercare%20facility%20that%20empowers%20young%20adults%20who%20have%20aged%20out%20of%C2%A0%20childcare%20institutions%20(CCIs).%20It%20offers%20them%20more%20than%20just%20shelter%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gives%20them%20dignity%2C%20purpose%2C%20and%20a%20path%20to%20self-reliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%20the%20first%20time%20you%20stepped%20out%20of%20your%20home%2C%20unsure%20of%20which%20college%20course%20to%20pick%2C%20struggling%20to%20find%20that%20first%20job%2C%20or%20save%20enough%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20space%20in%20a%20new%20city%3F%20Adulting%20is%20tough%20%E2%80%94%20filled%20with%20confusion%2C%20complexity%2C%20and%20countless%20moments%20of%20self-discovery.%20Now%2C%20imagine%20navigating%20this%20transition%20without%20a%20family%20or%20support%20system%2C%20often%20with%20the%20added%20burden%20of%20emotional%2C%20physical%2C%20or%20even%20sexual%20trauma.%20This%20is%20the%20reality%20for%20thousands%20of%20youth%20who%20are%20forced%20to%20leave%20childcare%20institutions%20once%20they%20turn%2018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20two%20bustling%20cities%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Chennai%2C%20the%20WeLive%20Foundation%20is%20reshaping%20how%20we%20think%20about%20young%20adults%20ageing%20out%20of%20government%20care.%20Over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20WeLive%20has%20empowered%20over%20175%20young%20people%20through%20its%20aftercare%20facility%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20shelter%20but%20by%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20skills%20and%20emotional%20resilience%20they%20need%20to%20find%20their%20footing%20in%20a%20world%20that%20can%20be%20unforgiving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20society%20that%20often%20overlooks%20these%20vulnerable%20young%20adults%2C%20WeLive%20has%20been%20making%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfiguring%20out%E2%80%9D%20phase%20of%20life%20a%20little%20easier%20for%20those%20who%20need%20it%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20lives%2C%20one%20step%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20WeLive%20began%20when%20one%20of%20its%20founders%2C%20a%20former%20CCI%20warden%2C%20saw%20firsthand%20the%20difficulties%20young%20adults%20faced%20upon%20leaving%20institutional%20care.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20few%20of%20them%20turned%2018%2C%20he%20took%20them%20into%20his%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Ramya%20Sundararajan%2C%20CEO%20of%20WeLive%20Foundation.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20experience%20sparked%20the%20idea%20for%20WeLive.%E2%80%9D%20The%20foundation%20opened%20its%20first%20centre%20for%20young%20men%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%20December%202020%2C%20with%20just%20five%20residents.%20Today%2C%20it%20has%20expanded%20to%20three%20residential%20programmes%20across%20Bengaluru%20and%20Chennai%2C%20supporting%20both%20men%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-med