lled%20in%20a%20study%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ramya.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20those%20who%20have%20passed%20their%2010th%20grade%2C%20we%20prepare%20them%20to%20complete%20their%2012th%20through%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS).%20If%20they%E2%80%99ve%20already%20matriculated%2C%20they%20pursue%20higher%20education%20in%20college.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20academic%20and%20professional%20development%20are%20only%20part%20of%20the%20equation.%20Ramya%20emphasises%20that%20these%20young%20adults%20often%20carry%20heavy%20emotional%20burdens.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20them%20have%20endured%20severe%20trauma%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20function%2C%20let%20alone%20focus%20on%20work%20or%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20This%20is%20why%20WeLive%20places%20equal%20importance%20on%20its%20well-being%20pillar%2C%20which%20offers%20counselling%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F231083%2Fmental-health-stress-depression-anxiety-covid-19-online-therapy-sessions-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epsychological%20support%2C%20and%20mentorshi%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F231083%2Fmental-health-stress-depression-anxiety-covid-19-online-therapy-sessions-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%3Ep%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20if%20a%20youth%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20good%20from%20within%2C%20it%20can%20be%20incredibly%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20hold%20down%20a%20job%20or%20excel%20in%20their%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramya%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelonging%20to%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018%20to%2023%2C%20these%20young%20care%20leavers%20from%20about%2010-12%20states%20of%20India%20are%20open%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20facility%20for%202-3%20years%20until%20they%20gain%20some%20work%20experience%2C%20education%20and%20savings%20to%20get%20back%20on%20their%20feet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamya%2C%20recalling%20the%20earlier%20days%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20started%2C%20our%20focus%20was%20on%20improving%20work%20readiness.%20It%20seemed%20straightforward%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20the%20youth%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F272114%2Fautobot-india-academy-provides-jobs-for-electric-vehicle-engineers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskilling%20and%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20streams%2C%20and%20helping%20them%20secure%20jobs.%20However%2C%20ensuring%20they%20stayed%20in%20these%20jobs%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20challenge.%20Many%2C%20like%20most%20of%20us%2C%20switch%20two%20or%20three%20jobs%20before%20settling%2C%20and%20guiding%20them%20through%20this%20process%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20support.%20Once%20we%20established%20partnerships%20with%20skill%20providers%20and%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20help%20them%20stick%20with%20their%20jobs%2C%20things%20began%20to%20fall%20into%20place.%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20culture%20of%20saving%20and%20investing%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20WeLive%E2%80%99s%20proudest%20achievements%20is%20the%20financial%20mindset%20shift%20among%20its%20residents.%20Over%2050%25%20of%20them%20are%20now%20investing%20in%20mutual%20funds%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rare%20feat%20even%20for%20young%20adults%20from%20stable%20backgrounds.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20many%20people%20in%20their%20late%2020s%20starting%20their%20investment%20journey%20takes%20time.%20But%20here%2C%20we%20have%2018%2C%2019-year-olds%20%E2%80%94%20first-time%20learners%20from%20disadvantaged%20backgrounds%20%E2%80%94%20investing%20in%20SBI%20and%20ICICI%20mutual%20funds%20through%20apps%20like%20PhonePe%20and%20Groww.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20investments%20range%20from%20Rs%202%2C500%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20giving%20them%20the%20financial%20foundation%20to%20live%20independently%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20culture%20of%20saving%20has%20become%20contagious.%20They%20now%20set%20financial%20goals%2C%20discussing%20targets%20like%20seasoned%20investors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344353%2Fwomen-in-finance-how-to-invest-stock-market-mutual-funds-monika-halan-mrin-agarwal-rachana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20focus%20on%20financial%20planning%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20part%20of%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20larger%20goal%3A%20empowering%20youth%20to%20become%20responsible%20decision-makers%2C%20both%20financially%20and%20emotionally.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20learning%20how%20to%20manage%20their%20lives%2C%20handle%20relationships%2C%20and%20navigate%20crises.%20We%E2%80%99re%20guiding%20them%20into%20adulthood%20they%20never%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_043_11zon-1-1729773144.jpg%3Ffit%3D3054%252C2038%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%223054%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22WeLive%20Foundation%20is%20working%20on%20empowering%20youth%20to%20become%20responsible%20decision-makers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_043_11zon-1-1729773144.jpg%3Fw%3D3054%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%203054w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_043_11zon-1-1729773144.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_043_11zon-1-1729773144.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C334%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterin