8%2Fworld-polio-day-inspiring-indians-chartered-accountant-doctor-entrepreneur%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Did%20Embracing%20ADHD%20Spark%20a%20Creative%20Breakthrough%20for%20This%20Writer%3F%20Tips%20for%20Work%20Success%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20deadlines%20loom%20and%20distractions%20abound%2C%20the%20struggle%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353745%2Fakash-muralidharan-masterchef-tamil-winner-vizha-medai-south-indian-food-adhd-ravioli-rasam-pongal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAttention%20Deficit%20Hyperactivity%20Disorder%20(ADHD)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecan%20leave%20individuals%20feeling%20isolated.%20For%20Aalen%20Issac%2C%20a%20senior%20content%20associate%20at%20Alyve%20Health%2C%20this%20battle%20has%20shaped%20his%20professional%20life%20and%20made%20him%20resilient%20in%20achieving%20his%20goals.%20Aalen%E2%80%99s%20journey%20with%20ADHD%20began%20long%20before%20his%20diagnosis%20at%20age%2024.%20He%20first%20encountered%20the%20term%20when%20his%20youngest%20brother%20was%20diagnosed%20as%20a%20child%2C%20prompting%20their%20family%20to%20consider%20testing%20for%20all%20the%20siblings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Aalen%20had%20struggled%20with%20attention%20issues%20growing%20up%2C%20he%20had%20never%20received%20a%20diagnosis%20before%20that.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20discusses%20his%20experience%20with%20ADHD%2C%20sharing%20the%20challenges%20he%20faces%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264065%2Fwhat-is-invisible-disability-workplace-autism-depression-adhd-policy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoping%20strategies%20he%20employs%20at%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20offers%20valuable%20insights%20for%20others%20with%20ADHD%20navigating%20the%20workspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experiencing%20difficulties%20with%20attention%20throughout%20his%20life%2C%20Aalen%20sought%20help%20for%20anxiety%20three%20years%20ago%20and%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20something%20known%20as%20executive%20dysfunction%2C%20and%20I%20learnt%20about%20it%20very%20late%20in%20life.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20mental%20block%20essentially.%20If%20there%20is%20something%20that%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20do%2C%20I%20simply%20cannot%20do%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20procrastination%3B%20I%20know%20I%20have%20to%20do%20it%2C%20but%20I%20cannot.%20Many%20people%20with%20ADHD%20struggle%20with%20deadlines%20and%20submitting%20assignments%20due%20to%20this%20reason.%20The%20brain%20just%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20function%20that%20way.%20Another%20problem%20I%20have%20is%20difficulty%20with%20attention%20to%20detail%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CADHD%20can%20often%20be%20identified%20in%20childhood%20or%20adolescence%2C%20and%20while%20it%20is%20manageable%2C%20getting%20diagnosed%20after%20entering%20the%20workforce%20can%20bring%20additional%20challenges.%20Adults%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%20may%20experience%20heightened%20anger%2C%20stress%2C%20and%20relationship%20issues%2C%20alongside%20reduced%20dynamism%20and%20good%20spirit%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pompa%20Maitra%20Chakraborty%2C%20a%20clinical%20psychologist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIdentifying%20the%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20coping%20mechanism%2C%20Aalen%20acknowledged%20his%20reliance%20on%20caffeine%2C%20which%20provides%20him%20with%20comfort%2C%20even%20though%20it%20may%20not%20be%20the%20healthiest%20option.%20%E2%80%9CI%20drink%20a%20lot%20of%20coffee%20that%20helps%20me%20get%20through%20the%20day.%20There%20is%20a%20brief%20window%20after%20having%20caffeine%20where%20I%20can%20focus%20better%20and%20be%20productive.%20However%2C%20I%20have%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20my%20coffee%20consumption%20has%20increased%20significantly%2C%20leading%20me%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20reflecting%20on%20other%20times%20he%20resorted%20to%20unhealthy%20coping%20mechanisms%2C%20such%20as%20smoking%2C%20which%20ultimately%20lead%20to%20breathing%20difficulties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recounts%20his%20experiences%20in%20managing%20distractions%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20discussing%20the%20strategies%20he%20employs%20to%20maintain%20focus%20amidst%20a%20busy%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20significant%20obstacle%20for%20me%2C%20as%20my%20work%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20writing%20and%20requires%20me%20to%20be%20in%20front%20of%20a%20screen%20constantly.%20I%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20focus%20when%20there%20are%20people%20around%20or%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20noise.%20While%20I%20struggle%20with%20concentration%20in%20general%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20distractions%20makes%20it%20even%20more%20challenging.%20To%20combat%20this%2C%20I%20use%20noise-cancelling%20headphones%20to%20minimise%20ambient%20noise.%20If%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20those%2C%20I%20always%20keep%20my%20earphones%20handy%2C%20which%20helps%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aalen%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20540px)%20100vw%2C%20540px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Ffit%3D500%252C645%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aalen%20Isaac%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Fw%3D540%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20540w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-2