india.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-27-at-8.32.55-PM_11zon-1729604240.jpeg%3Fresize%3D150%252C68%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371681%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKhagembam%20Indrakumar%20Singh%20interacts%20with%20his%20students%20during%20one%20of%20his%20Sunday%20Campaigns.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20of%20selfless%20pursuit%2C%20in%202013%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Government%20recognised%20Indrakumar%E2%80%99s%20service%20and%20honoured%20him%20with%20the%20State%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Award.%20The%20accolade%20reinvigorated%20his%20drive%2C%20leading%20him%20to%20start%20a%20new%20initiative%20%E2%80%94%20an%20annual%20constituency-based%20competition%20for%20students%20every%20December%2C%20including%20essays%2C%20quizzes%2C%20maths%2C%20and%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrivate%20school%20students%20often%20have%20infrastructural%20advantages.%20My%20father%20wanted%20government%20school%20students%20to%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20on%20par%20with%20others.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20he%20started%20the%20competition%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chinglensana%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20in%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20footsteps%2C%20Chinglensana%20is%20pursuing%20a%20career%20aimed%20at%20educating%20and%20training%20children.%20His%20current%20position%20at%20%E2%80%98Lend%20A%20Hand%2C%20India%E2%80%99%20allows%20him%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20vocational%20training%20module%20for%20children%20in%20Nagaland.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20to%20gather%20the%20necessary%20experience%20so%20that%20I%20can%20help%20my%20father%20in%20a%20better%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAddressing%20student%20dropout%20rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20school%20was%20upgraded%20to%20an%20upper%20primary%20school%3B