s%20of%20snow%20leopard%20habitat%20in%20India%20is%20legally%20protected.%20Less%20than%2070%25%20of%20this%20predator%E2%80%99s%20habitat%20remains%20unprotected.%20%3Cem%3E(Above%20images%20of%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20a%20snow%20leopard%20%26amp%3B%20Charudutt%20Mishra)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20figures%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20for%20local%20communities%20to%20be%20engaged%20in%20the%20conservation%20of%20this%20threatened%20species.%20Here%20are%20eight%20conservationists%20who%20have%20done%20incredible%20work%20in%20not%20only%20understanding%20snow%20leopards%20but%20also%20engaging%20local%20communities%20to%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECharudutt%20Mishra%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharudutt%20Mishra%20(Charu)%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%2C%20is%20considered%20by%20many%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20expert%20on%20snow%20leopard%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20pioneer%20of%20the%20community-based%20conservation%20model%20and%20has%20spent%20nearly%20three%20decades%20spearheading%20groundbreaking%20projects.%20In%201997%2C%20he%20embarked%20upon%20a%20PhD%20in%20the%20remote%20village%20of%20Kibber%2C%20in%20Spiti%20Valley%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20Upon%20reaching%20there%2C%20he%20heard%20a%20disturbing%20story%20that%20a%20snow%20leopard%20had%20recently%20been%20mercilessly%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20letting%20anger%20or%20distrust%20get%20in%20the%20way%2C%20Charu%20immersed%20himself%20in%20the%20community%20and%20took%20the%20time%20to%20understand%20the%20hardships%20under%20which%20they%20lived.%20He%20learnt%20that%20local%20communities%20were%20not%20unwilling%20but%20unable%20to%20%E2%80%9Cactually%20participate%20in%20conservation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20sr