0of%20snow%20leopards.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20Khenrab%20also%20felt%20when%20he%20was%2012%20and%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20this%20vivid%20memory%20he%20had%20of%20a%20snow%20leopard%20would%20inspire%20Khenrab%20to%20dedicate%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life%20to%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20joining%20the%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Department%20in%202000%2C%20he%20has%20rescued%20about%2050%20snow%20leopards%20trapped%20in%20human%20habitations%20and%20released%20them%20back%20into%20the%20wild.%20An%20expert%20in%20installing%20camera%20traps%20and%20tracking%2C%20he%20also%20consults%20private%20operators%20on%20how%20to%20plan%20snow%20leopard%20expeditions%2C%20train%20spotters%20and%20trackers%2C%20and%20leave%20behind%20a%20minimal%20ecological%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKarma%20Sonam%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264378%2Fkarma-sonam-natwest-group-earth-heroes-award-snow-leopard-himalayan-wolf-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKarma%20Sonam%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20field%20manager%20with%20the%20Nature%20Conservation%20Foundation%20(NCF)%20in%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%94%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20reducing%20human-wildlife%20conflict%20in%2017%20communities%20across%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20and%20creating%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20environmental%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeveraging%20a%20system%20of%20community-based%20conservation%2C%20he%20has%20facilitated%20the%20implementation%20of%20critical%20initiatives%20like%20self-sustaining%20insurance%20schemes%20for%20pastoralists%20who%20lose%20their%20livestock%20to%20predators%20like%20snow%20leopards%2C%20creation%20of%20grazing-free%20reserves%20for%20herbivores%20like%20the%20Tibetan%20gazelle%20(that%20are%20prey%20for%20snow%20leopards)%2C%20and%20converting%20Shandongs%20(traditional%20wolf%20traps)%20into%20holy%20Buddhist%20sites%20that%20allow%20trapped%20animals%20to%20escape%20back%20into%20the%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FIMG-20211012-WA0011-500x889.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karma%20Sonam%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FIMG-20211012-WA0011-500x889.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FIMG-20211012-WA0011-169x300.jpg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FIMG-20211012-WA0011.jpg%20720w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-264391%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKarma%20Sonam%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20worked%20for%20Karma%20is%20his%20natural%20ability%20to%20build%20and%20maintain%20close%20relationships%20with%20different%20communities.%20Leveraging%20these%20close%20relationships%2C%20he%20convinces%20and%20incentivises%20local%20communities%20to%20work%20for%20wildlife%20conservation.%20For%20decades%2C%20pastoralists%20in%20Ladakh%20have%20had%20a%20difficult%20relationship%20with%20predators%2C%20like%20snow%20leopards%20and%20wolves%2C%20who%20prey%20on%20their%20livestock.%20Through%20his%20extensive%20grassroots%20efforts%2C%20he%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20to%20repair%20that%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKoustubh%20Sharma%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoustubh%20Sharma%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Conservation%20Science%20Director%20at%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%20%E2%80%94%20has%20worked%20in%20some%20of%20the%20remotest%20and%20roughest%20terrains%20in%20the%20world%20to%20better%20understand%20snow%20leopard%20ecology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntroduced%20to%20them%20by%20Dr%20Raghu%20Chundawat%2C%20a%20pioneer%20of%20snow%20leopard%20studies%20in%20India%2C%20Koustubh%20has%20dedicated%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20time%20to%20the%20Global%20Snow%20Leopard%20and%20Ecosystem%20Protection%20Programme.%20The%20programme%2C%20according%20to%20Koustubh%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbrings%20together%20governments%20from%2012%20snow%20leopard%20range%20countries%2C%20policymakers%2C%20institutions%2C%20organisations%20and%20conservationists%20toward%20securing%20the%20future%20of%20snow%20leopards%20and%20their%20mountains%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905-300x238.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905-500x396.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905-768x608.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905-150x119.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371719%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20wish%20more%20people%20knew%20about%20conservation%20initiatives%20is%20that%20not%20a%20single%20penny%20of%20the%20money%20meant%20for%20snow%20leopard%20conservation%20goes%20into%20the%20pocket%20of%20the%20snow%20leopards.%20It%20is%20always%20invested%20in%20support%20of%20people%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20local%20or%20indigenous%20communities%20running%20conservation%20programmes%2C%20the%20frontline%20rangers%20patrolling%20and%20monitoring%20wildlife%2C%20or%20the%20conservation%20teams%20working%20under%20expedition%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Koustubh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6our%20initiatives%20are%20about%20much%20more%20than%20just%20protecting%20a%20single%20species.%20We%20work%20closely%20with%20local%20and%20indigenous%20communities%20to%20create%20sustainable%20livelihoods%20that%20benefit%20both%20people%20and%20wildlife.%20When%20we%20invest%20in%20conservation%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20investing%20in%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanctuarynaturefoundation.org%2Farticle%2Fmeet-koustubh-sharma%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanctuary%20Nature%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsnowleopard.org%2Fmeet-snow-leopard-trusts-new-conservation-science-director-dr-koustubh-sharma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EShiv%20Kumar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20evening%20in%202019%20when%20Shiv%20Kumar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Deputy%20Range%20Officer%20at%20Lahaul%20forest%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20first%20spotted%20a%20snow%20leopard.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F274641%2Fforest-guard-officer-photographs-snow-leopard-conservation-himachal-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20he%20called%20it%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunforgettable%20moment%E2%80%9D.%20Thereafter%2C%20Shiv%20began%20conservation%20awareness%20classes%20about%20snow%20leopards%20among%20school%20children%20for%20the%20animal%E2%80%99s%20protection.%20He%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20villagers%20to%20inform%20them%20about%20its%20importance%2C%20threatened%20existence%20and%20its%20need%20for%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20livestock%20belonging%20to%20the%20Gaddi%20community%20%E2%80%94%20a%20community%20of%20migratory%20shepherds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20locals%20in%20the%20Lahaul%20area%20remain%20under%20threat%20from%20snow%20leopards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2FShiv-Kumar-1643638321.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shiv%20Kumar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2FShiv-Kumar-1643638321.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2FShiv-Kumar-1643638321-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2FShiv-Kumar-1643638321-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2FShiv-Kumar-1643638321-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2FShiv-Kumar-1643638321-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-274656%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShiv%20Kumar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fynnchennai.weebly.com%2Find-shiv-kumar.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChennai%20Young%20Naturalists%E2%80%99%20Network%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shiv%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COften%2C%20people%20from%20this%20%5BGaddi%5D%20community%20did%20not%20apply%20for%20compensation%20even%20when%20they%20lost%20livestock%20because%20the%20alpine%20meadows%20they%20used%20to%20graze%20their%20livestock%20in%20would%20be%2030%20to%2035%20kilometres%20from%20the%20nearest%20town.%20So%20we%20got%20together%20with%20the%20Nature%20Conservation%20Foundation%20(NCF)%20and%20made%20a%20manual%20with%20all%20the%20procedures%20to%20follow%20if%20one%20were%20to%20lose%20any%20livestock.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaramjeet%2Fstatus%2F1792108597637476542%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKaramjeet%20Singh%2FX%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Whitley%20Fund%20for%20Nature)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729608170000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D371701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20International%20Snow%20Leopard%20Day%2C%20we%20highlight%20the%20contributions%20of%20eight%20conservationists%20who%20have%20dedicated%20their%20lives%20to%20protecting%20this%20elusive%20wild%20cat%20by%20ethically%20and%20effectively%20engaging%20with%20local%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F371701%2Finternational-snow-leopard-day-conservationists-in-india-charudutt-mishra-tsewang-namgail%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%20Techie%20Turns%20Organic%20Farmer%2C%20Builds%20a%20Profitable%20Moringa%20Business%20With%20His%20Wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20over%20two%20decades%20that%20Jitender%20Mann%20spent%20in%20cities%20like%20Chennai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Delhi%2C%20he%20observed%20a%20concerning%20trend%3A%20rising%20rates%20of%20health%20issues%20among%20both%20young%20and%20elderly%20residents%3B%20thyroid%20disorders%20and%20high%20blood%20pressure%20appeared%20to%20Jitender%20as%20a%20common%20occurrence%20in%20urban%20areas.%20He%2C%20himself%2C%20was%20no%20exception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20workaholic%20during%20my%20early%2020s%2C%20often%20being%20the%20last%20one%20to%20leave%20office%20at%201%20am.%20By%20my%20early%2040s%2C%20I%20was%20suffering%20from%20high%20blood%20pressure%20(BP)%20and%20extreme%20joint%20pains.%20I%20would%20commute%20via%20the%20metro%20and%20sit%20all%20day%20at%20a%20desk.%20I%20felt%20healthy%2C%20but%20once%20I%20started%20medication%20for%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20I%20realised%20I%20was%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20blood%20pressure%20was%20160.%20It%20was%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20me.%20After%20starting%20the%20medication%2C%20I%20felt%20that%20this%20was%20going%20to%20be%20my%20new%20normal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20the%20Laxmi%20Nagar%20area%20near%20the%20Yamuna%20river%2C%20he%20often%20witnessed%20farmers%20using%20polluted%20water%20to%20irrigate%20their%20fields.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20Delhi%20consumes%20food%20produced%20in%20those%20fields.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20only%20a%20few%20elderly%20people%20would%20complain%20of%20joint%20pains%2C%20but%20these%20days%2C%20even%20young%20people%20and%20toddlers%20are%20experiencing%20blood%20glucose%20issues.%20I%20am%20not%20an%20expert%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20everything%20is%20related%20to%20the%20food%20we%20eat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jitender%20and%20Sarla%20have%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20by%20selling%20moringa%20powder.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371317%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJitender%20and%20Sarla%20have%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20by%20selling%20moringa%20powder.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20an%20ICMR%20(Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research)%20report%20had%20revealed%20that%20an%20estimated%2056.4%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20disease%20burden%20was%20linked%20to%20unhealthy%20diets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitender%E2%80%99s%20realisation%20fueled%20his%20determination%20to%20move%20back%20to%20his%20ancestral%20home%20in%20Mehmudpur%20village%20in%20Sonipat%20district%20of%20Haryana%2C%20alongside%20his%20wife%2C%20Sarla.%20In%202018%2C%20after%20working%20for%2011%20years%20at%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20(TCS)%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20farmer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20gradually%20explored%20the%20healing%20properties%20of%20moringa%20and%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20to%20promote%20its%20potential%20health%20benefits.%20Today%2C%20they%20have%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20by%20selling%20moringa%20powder%20to%20urban%20consumers%20in%20cities%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETapping%20into%20%E2%80%98miraculous%20benefits%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%202015%2C%20during%20his%20stay%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Jitender%20first%20started%20growing%20moringa%20on%20the%20terrace%20of%20his%20home.%20%E2%80%9CI%20developed%20a%20lush%20green%20garden%20with%20vegetables%20such%20as%20ridge%20gourd%2C%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20and%20moringa%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImpressed%20by%20the%20results%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20replace%20their%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20fields%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F303221%2Fkerala-engineer-turned-farmer-starts-moringa-mango-organic-farm-in-melbourne-australia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoringa%20farm%20%3C%2Fa%3Eafter%20moving%20to%20their%20village.%20Starting%20with%20two%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20the%20couple%20gradually%20expanded%20their%20production%20to%20four%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20titled%20%E2%80%98Moringa%20oleifera%3A%20An%20Updated%20Comprehensive%20Review%20of%20Its%20Pharmacological%20Activities%2C%20Ethnomedicinal%2C%20Phytopharmaceutical%20Formulation%2C%20Clinical%2C%20Phytochemical%2C%20and%20Toxicological%20Aspects%E2%80%99%2C%20published%20in%20PubMed%20Central%20(PMC)%2C%20observed%20that%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282661%2Fkerala-woman-entrepreneur-makes-healthy-millet-flour-from-moringa-jackfruit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20moringa%20oleifera%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctree%20of%20life%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cmiracle%20tree%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20was%20effective%20in%20treating%20wounds%2C%20pain%2C%20ulcers%2C%20liver%20disease%2C%20heart%20disease%2C%20cancer%2C%20and%20inflammation%3B%20it%20was%20also%20proved%20to%20be%20beneficial%20in%20lowering%20glucose%20levels.%20As%20per%20the%20same%20study%2C%20moringa%20leaves%20are%20a%20quick%20remedy%20for%20inflammatory%20conditions%20such%20as%20glandular%20inflammation%2C%20headache%2C%20and%20bronchitis.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20miraculous%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20exclaims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20ensures%20that%20the%20nutritional%20content%20of%20the%20leaves%20remains%20in%20the%20final%20product%20for%20distribution.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371318%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20ensures%20that%20the%20nutritional%20content%20of%20the%20leaves%20remains%20in%20the%20final%20product%20for%20distribution.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20moringa%20leaves%2C%20Jitender%20and%20Sarla%20invested%20in%20a%20state-of-the-art%20drying%20setup%20that%20ensures%20optimal%20drying%20conditions%20while%20retaining%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20beneficial%20properties.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20plucking%20stems%20with%20leaves%2C%20we%20wash%20them%20twice%20and%20bundle%20seven%20to%20nine%20stems%20together%20so%20that%20each%20leaf%20is%20separated%20for%20easier%20drying%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarla%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20dry%20the%20leaves%20under%20large%20fans%20and%20also%20in%20a%20controlled%20greenhouse%20setup%2C%20where%20energy%20gets%20trapped%20and%20the%20temperature%20is%208-10%20degrees%20hotter%20than%20outside.%20After%2012%20hours%2C%20the%20leaves%20become%20crunchy%20and%20we%20separate%20them%20from%20the%20stems.%20We%20then%20make%20a%20coarse%20powder%20in%20a%20pulveriser%20and%20remove%20stalks%20before%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20meticulous%20process%2C%20Jitender%20says%2C%20ensures%20that%20the%20nutritional%20content%20of%20the%20leaves%20remains%20in%20the%20final%20product%20for%20distribution.%20%E2%80%9CMoringa%20is%20a%20summer-loving%20plant%20in%20North%20India.%20We%20harvest%20leaves%20for%20about%20seven%20months%20between%20April%20and%20October%2C%20with%20the%20plant%20remaining%20dormant%20for%20the%20remaining%20five%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarla%20points%20out%20that%20to%20ensure%20high-quality%20crop%20production%2C%20they%20adopted%20a%20jungle%20farming%20method.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20method%2C%20we%20do%20not%20till%20the%20soil%20and%20use%20weeds%20and%20other%20leaves%20as%20mulch.%20We%20also%20avoid%20harmful%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20pesticides%2C%20and%20weedicides.%20This%20ensures%20that%20our%20soil%20has%20good%20aeration%20and%20high%20carbon%20content.%20You%20can%20only%20produce%20good-quality%20moringa%20leaves%20if%20your%20soil%20is%20fertile%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20to%20becoming%20a%20profitable%20venture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarla%20informs%20that%20about%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20dry%20powder%20can%20be%20produced%20from%20one%20acre%20of%20land.%20By%20selling%20a%20200-gram%20packet%20of%20moringa%20powder%2C%20the%20couple%20earns%20Rs%20650.%20On%20average%2C%20they%20make%20sales%20of%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20per%20month%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20per%20acre%20every%20season.%20They%20established%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20metro%20cities%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Gurugram%20primarily%20through%20word%20of%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20with%20two%20acres%20for%20cultivating%20moringa%20powder%2C%20but%20our%20demand%20is%20growing%20at%20twice%20the%20rate%20of%20our%20production.%20Next%20year%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20expand%20our%20moringa%20fields%20from%20four%20to%20eight%20acres%20and%20explore%20international%20markets%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20employs%20many%20rural%20women%20to%20pluck%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20package%20moringa%20leaves%20powder.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3