ment-caption%5C%22%3EChef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20created%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20in%20New%20York%20as%20an%20ode%20to%20street%20vendors%20of%20India%20and%20the%20food%20he%20grew%20up%20eating%20in%20Amritsar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20positively%20brimming%20with%20joy%20to%20announce%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebarfis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehad%20the%20desired%20effect%3B%20as%20many%20Indian%20immigrants%20found%20themselves%20transported%20by%20the%20mini%20square-shaped%20time%20capsules%20from%20America%20to%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20festive%20madness%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevered%20on%20the%20culinary%20circuit%2C%20Vikas%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20prowess%20transcends%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20multi-hyphenate%20has%20authored%20over%2037%20books%20%E2%80%94%20with%20his%20most%20recent%20%E2%80%98Imaginary%20Rain%E2%80%99%20(2023)%20being%20turned%20into%20a%20Shabana%20Azmi%20starrer%20%E2%80%94%20has%20directed%20three%20films%20and%20two%20documentaries%3B%20been%20one%20of%20the%20judges%20at%20MasterChef%20India%3B%20and%20helmed%20several%20restaurants%20including%20New%20York%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20%E2%80%98Junoon%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20restaurants%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357879%2Fmichelin-star-indian-restaurants-avatara-junoon-gaa-veeraswamy-gymkhana-rania-tamarind-semma-benares%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceive%20the%20coveted%20Michelin%20star%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20this%20compelling%20bio%2C%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20primary%20identifier%20is%20that%20of%20a%20proud%20Indian.%20And%20this%20is%20reflected%20in%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Etadka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spices%20heated%20in%20hot%20oil)%20that%20makes%20its%20way%20into%20his%20curries%20to%20the%20sparkle%20in%20his%20eyes%20when%20he%20speaks%20about%20life%20back%20in%20his%20beloved%20hometown%2C%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20Vikas%20Khanna%2C%20all%20roads%20lead%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhanna%E2%80%99s%20culinary%20mind%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20occupy%20it.%20Memories%20of%20serving%20the%20who%E2%80%99s%20who%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20he%20has%20been%20the%20%3Cem%3Echef%20du%20jour%3C%2Fem%3E%20multiple%20times%20for%20the%20Obama%20family%2C%20while%20also%20working%20closely%20with%20food%20mogul%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20%E2%80%94%20find%20space%20right%20next%20to%20nostalgic%20memories%20of%20binge%20sessions%20involving%20rounds%20of%20%3Cem%3Etikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(potato%20patties)%20from%20%E2%80%98Mathura%20ki%20Tikki%E2%80%99%20in%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Among%20Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna's%20fondest%20memories%20are%20those%20with%20his%20family%20and%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20in%20Amritsar%2C%20his%20hometown%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371662%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmong%20Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20fondest%20memories%20are%20those%20with%20his%20family%20and%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20in%20Amritsar%2C%20his%20hometown%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20distinctly%20remember%20how%20this%20%5B%3Cem%3Etikki%3C%2Fem%3E%5D%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F193273%2Flifestyle-health-street-food-recipes-millet-dosa-bhel-puri-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavourite%20snack%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20my%20cousins%20who%20would%20visit%20us%20from%20Kolkata%20and%20Mumbai.%20Nothing%20was%20done%20to%20make%20the%20potatoes%20crisp.%20Instead%2C%20they%20were%20fried%20to%20a%20great%20degree%20and%20then%20pressed%20on%20a%20hot%20%3Cem%3Etava%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pan)%20laden%20with%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20the%20late%2070s%2C%20each%20%3Cem%3Etikki%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20around%20Rs%2020%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20money!%20But%20the%20crispiness%20of%20those%20potatoes%20is%20very%20nostalgic%20for%20me.%20I%20still%20snack%20on%20them%20when%20I%20go%20to%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Khanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99d%20be%20interested%20to%20know%20that%20this%20spot%20is%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20distinguished%20ones%20dotting%20the%20%E2%80%98food%20map%E2%80%99%20devised%20by%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20mother%20to%20celebrate%20his%20homecoming.%20The%20locales%20are%20set%20in%20stone%20and%20nothing%20is%20up%20for%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20global%20fame%20means%20the%20duo%20can%20no%20longer%20feast%20on%20%3Cem%3Etikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246397%2Fstreet-food-vendors-pav-bhaji-american-civil-war-cotton-mill-portugese-mumbai-video-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estreet%20food)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20peace%20without%20500-odd%20people%20thronging%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20their%20favourite%20chef%20or%20(if%20they%E2%80%99re%20lucky)%20a%20selfie.%20And%20Khanna%20is%20ever-obliging%2C%20animatedly%20chatting%20up%20each%20vendor%20he%20visits.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20all%2C%20they%20were%20my%20foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20perfectly%20segues%20his%20next%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20take%20things%20for%20granted%20when%20we%20have%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20treasures%20his%20earliest%20memories%20of%20feasting%20on%20the%20food%20prepared%20by%20his%20grandmother%20and%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20experiences%20that%20he%20will%20remember%20forever%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371666%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20treasures%20his%20earliest%20memories%20of%20feasting%20on%20the%20food%20prepared%20by%20his%20grandmother%20and%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20experiences%20that%20he%20will%20remember%20forever%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%