EThe%20couple%20has%20also%20observed%20the%20impact%20of%20climate%20change%20during%20their%20travels%2C%20prompting%20a%20new%20mission.%20Seven%20months%20ago%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20plant%2010%2C000%20saplings%20across%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20last%20three%20summers%20have%20been%20extremely%20hot%2C%20making%20staying%20outdoors%20very%20difficult.%20We%20wanted%20to%20take%20some%20steps%20to%20remedy%20this.%20Each%20of%20us%20needs%20to%20take%20some%20steps%20to%20fight%20climate%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sangeeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%E2%80%99ve%20successfully%20planted%20these%2010%2C000%20saplings%2C%20and%20now%20they%20have%20a%20loftier%20ambition%3A%20to%20plant%20one%20lakh%20saplings%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20travelling%20changed%20their%20perspective%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20sets%20this%20couple%20apart%20is%20their%20approach%20to%20travel.%20They%20go%20to%20remote%20locations%2C%20shunning%20the%20typical%20%E2%80%98touristy%E2%80%99%20places.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20explore%20the%20unexplored.%20This%20mindset%20shift%20has%20led%20to%20profound%20realisations%20about%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20their%20favourite%20location%2C%20the%20couple%20unanimously%20picks%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20for%20its%20natural%20beauty%20and%20welcoming%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC60b_hpPrvI%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC60b_hpPrvI%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2F