nd%20a%20good%20bathroom%20or%20dealing%20with%20the%20constant%20stares%20of%20men.%20Camping%20in%20the%20open%20also%20invites%20wildlife%20encounters%3B%20they%E2%80%99ve%20even%20had%20visits%20from%20leopards!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20once%20camped%20in%20Munsiyari%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20in%20an%20open%2C%20isolated%20area.%20Our%20dog%20Drogo%20sensed%20something%20approaching%20and%20started%20to%20panic.%20Our%20car%20has%20motion%20sensor%20lights%20that%20attracted%20a%20leopard.%20It%20came%20very%20close%2C%20and%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sleep%20that%20entire%20night.%20When%20we%20spoke%20to%20the%20villagers%20the%20next%20day%2C%20they%20said%20he%20is%20a%20regular%20visitor%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sangeeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-99-1729585966.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22They%20camp%20in%20remote%20villages%20across%20the%20country%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-99-1729585966.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-99-1729585966-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-99-1729585966-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-99-1729585966-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-99-1729585966-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371600%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThey%20camp%20in%20remote%20villages%20across%20the%20country%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20o